promptPrefix:

5 columns for the dimensions: 
- Search intent (informational, transactional, navegational...)
- Funnel segment (awareness, consideration, conversion...)
- Short-tail keywords
- Medium-tail keywwords

The keywords need to be generated in [TARGETLANGUAGE]
[PROMPT]
title: Keyword cluster generator
